Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有一天 從天空掉下來一個蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏給這顆蛋中孵出的不可思議的生物命名為毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它對夏來說是新的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與此同時 評議院在各公會之間建立了交換留學生制度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利用這個機會 在各公會之間四處詢問有關毛毛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻完全沒有得到有用的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這時 一行人受到評議院的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和劍齒之虎一起調查在近海處突然出現的神秘島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,評議院的判斷是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是個島嶼非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 已經祝福好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 到底有什麼危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個島上有未知生物的生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是人還是動物的奇怪的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產生於出現僅有幾天的島嶼上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一說的話 感覺確實有點危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才讓我們去探查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠岸後 我作為指揮官留在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陸後 有什麼情況就發信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.68,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}你來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近才出現的島嶼為什麼會有路？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是這個島以前有人類住過 但是後來沉沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在 又突然浮上來了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 那個遺跡裏說不定有什麼線索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得散發著一股很可疑的氣息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們分散開 調查一下周圍的情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個遺跡處匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 只是個森林嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱開始肚子餓了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 完全沒有緊張感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在森林中會有貝殼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個貝殼有見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇姬之鱗的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個石板背面的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 大家看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這個就是在人魚之踵那裏看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魚哎 看起來好好吃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會吃壞肚子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是海裏的東西連同島嶼一起上來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果之前這個島是沉入海中的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼樹木還能長得這麼繁茂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還形成了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏非比尋常這一點是毋庸置疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遺跡的方向 我們快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙就是生命反應的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 是海蛇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海裏的怪物 以前我曾經聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是陸地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 妖精的尾巴和劍齒之虎已經登陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快點前往那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩護 準備炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎 夏他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個遺跡中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在外面的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 被關在裏面了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的聲音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是心臟跳動的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是有什麼東西 在這裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們也得想辦法牽制一下那傢伙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 否則夏他們在裏面的會被壓扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰加農炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是斯汀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這個 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鳩拉給我們看的一樣的古代文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼…身體…動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被攻擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蘭巴爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就倒下了 完全不知道怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你將她們帶去船上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 但是你們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那麼多 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 再不快點就要被壓扁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 但是有那麼多的文字…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有點像心臟的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇 這個煙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛 你是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好噁心 頭好暈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎他們正在和怪物交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 說是突然就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這個情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼病毒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這兩個人搬到船艙裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那裏也寫著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「光」「恩惠」「樹木」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守護」「災禍」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「毒」「淨化」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒？淨化？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒？這個是毒氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 照一下天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在蛇姬之鱗看見的文獻畫的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏他們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子不能動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍的翼擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得可能會有什麼線索 就從蛇姬之鱗借出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個形狀 還有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和蛇姬之鱗那裏的石板是一個形狀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然表面的單詞少了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也許這麼做就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點啊 拉哈爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這座島沉下去吧…去聯繫評議院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須阻止病毒感染擴散到大陸去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:12:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果連你都被感染了的話 還有誰去傳達消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位…快點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 這個是植物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「光」「恩惠」「樹木」「光合作用」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「毒」「災厄」「淨化」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是「植物」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守護」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛？難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛修 雷庫塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 完全站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個難道是病毒什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我是誰 我該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然想到未來我會很害怕 但我會站出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為夏是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說我是「家人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個煙果然有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 那個煙不是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也在那裏面碰到了煙 但是沒被感染
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛身體裏出來的煙 才不是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出病毒的是這個島本身 那個是淨化病毒的煙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淨化？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是毛毛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛應該不是動物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛一定是淨化病毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙一直在保護我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛 我們可不會讓你一個人搶風頭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它看看我們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座島自古以來就不斷地上浮和下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而每當其上浮的時候 就會放出病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古代曾經有毫不知情的人在這座島上建立了文明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一直在幫助這些人的 就是毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼難道現在也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是一直在持續淨化病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮爆炎刃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在島上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 毛毛 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了 夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島開始下沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 毛毛 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了啊 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…會說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都忘了 但是 現在想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,語言和職責
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職責？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快起來 一起回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體已經和樹木一體化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和這個島一起沉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來把島上的病毒吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏就和大家一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不能再繼續守護大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃走吧 是離別的時候了 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是離別啊 我不可能走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 我也是…妖精的尾巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的一員吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是妖精的尾巴的同伴 是我們的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…我很開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 回答我 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛的…種子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能守護好那傢伙 明明是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和遺跡上記載的古代文明那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛是類似於那座島的神明一樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 而它也完成了自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 還會再會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了關門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今天能有工作做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,855)}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 快來救救咱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 你變成蓬蓬頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.66,0:24:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜電太厲害結果就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺適合你的 就這樣不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話了 夏也來幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 電到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 拜這個所賜我想到了個好點子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是電所以腦袋裏的燈泡亮了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆般的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是蓬蓬頭的哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那乾脆就叫蓬蓬比怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 名字什麼的怎麼樣都無所謂啦

